text: Luna I qui natus fuerit, uitalis eritse þe acenned bið liflic he bið.
Luna secunda, mediocris eritmedeme he bið.
Luna tertia, infirmus erituntrum he bið.
Luna IIII, tractatus regnum erittrahtnere cyninga he bið.
Luna V, iuuenis tolleturgeog he bið genumen.
Luna sexta, uitalis eritliflic he bið.
Luna VII, uitalis et utilis eritliflic & notwurðe he bið.
Luna VIII iuuenis decidetgeog he afealleð.
Luna IX, omnium adquisitor eritealra strinend he bið.
Luna X circuibit multa regioneshe abuten færð fela rica.
Luna XI, omnium adquisitor eritealra strinend he bið.
Luna XII, reliosus eritæwfæst he bið.
Luna XIII, aduersus impeditor eritwiðerweard letted he bið.
Luna XIIII, omnium tractator eritealra trahtnere he bið.
Luna XV, iuuenis morieturgeog swylt.
Luna XVI, uitalis et pauper eritliflic & þearfa he bið.
Luna XVIII, non diu uiuetna lange he ne leofað.
Luna XIX, in honore eriton wyrðscipe he bið.
Luna XX, bellator eritfeohtere he bið.
Luna XXI, latro ingeniosus eritsceaþa þancful he bið.
Luna XXII, laboriosus eritgeswincful he bið.
Luna XXIII, uulgarus eritwidcuð he bið.
Luna XXIIII, copios eritgenihtsum he bið.
Luna XXV, pericula multa patieturfræcnyssa feala he þolað.
Luna XXVI, nec diues nec pauper eritna welig na wædla he bið.
Luna XXVII, amicus eritfreond he bið.
Luna XXVIII, neglegens eritgimeleas he bið.
Luna XXVIIII, bonus et prouisor eritgod & forsceawere he bið.
Luna XXX, negotia multa tractabitceapa feala he asmeað.
